BCrypt Encryption: We have moved from SHA-256 to BCrypt, the industry standard for password security.
IP Limits: Added a limit to the number of accounts allowed per IP address to prevent spam/alts.
Mandatory Encryption: Security is no longer optional; it is always on.
  
‚ú® Player Experience (QoL)
Session Management: Disconnected? You can now rejoin within a few minutes without needing to type your password again!
Visual Improvements: Added a Blindness effect and a live Action Bar Countdown during the login phase for better immersion.
Teleportation System: You will now be automatically teleported to a safe spawn point upon joining and returned to your last location after logging in.
Tab Completion: Commands like /login and /register now support smoother auto-completion.
  
